Happy Daiquiri Day
.
The Lovers Daiquiri
.
When David Cordoba creates rum with daiquiri in mind you can expect something exciting
.
 The Lovers Daiquiri ( Perfect Daiquiri )
.
60 ml The Lovers Rum
30 ml Fresh Lime Juice
2  tsps Sugar (preferably from Sugar Cane)
.
Method: 
Place all ingredients into a cocktail shaker
Stir well until the sugar has dissolved
Fill shaker with cubed and crushed ice (half/half)
Shake  until the shaker is frozen.
Double strain into a pre-chilled glass.
.
PS “Never use lemon juice. And Remember please, that a too sweet Daiquiri is like a lovely lady with too much perfume” –
.
Charles H. Baker Jr.
.

Suelo al Alma or Soil to Soul for #ZeroWasteMonth with Flor de Cana rum. 
.
Inspired by the indigenous people and they sustainable way of living. 
.
The connection between people and earth. 
The cocktail is made with sustainable product and using fruit waste. 
Flor De Cana 12, Coconut rum,  Chocolate Wine, Pineapple skin spiced syrup, berry water and Cassis Bitters. Pineapple skin foam on the top and candy made from the berries left from the Berry water. 
Served in highball cut from a bottle and temple vessel made from coconut husk and waste material.
.
